abstract: Everything I’ve done with my body, from top surgery to gradual low-dose testosterone to a hysterectomy, was, at some point, a revelation.

headline_main: Transgender Lives: Your Stories: Joni Christian

abstract: For transgender people of all walks of life, nothing matches the devastation of seeing someone who used to respect you come to see you as an insect.

headline_main: Transgender Lives: Your Stories: Greyson Simon

abstract: The relative ease with which I found resources and care, in a city with a large trans community, makes me feel grateful and humbled.
